Date Format : YYYY-MM-DD

* Version 0.5.0 -- 2011-11-06

	* Better update thread, no more freeze after a while
	* Proxy support
	* update waterline with 'w' to display a line for the last read
	* Bugs fixed

* Version 0.4.2 -- 2011-09-20

	* Retweet counter
	* Relative time now update correctly
	* Few default values changed
	* Better display with waterline
	* Force DM reply if you are in DM timeline
	* Compress param rename to compact
	* New header template in params

* Version 0.4.1 -- 2011-07-27

	* Goo.gl shortener service added.
	* Musd.pl shortener service added. (Hobbestigrou contribution)
	* Logging system added, with customizable verbosity, stored in
	~/.config/tyrs/tyrs.log
	* New curstomer_key and customer_secret params for own StatusNet instance.
	* Doc and help screen updated
	* Draw a line to mark your last tweets read in previous session
	* Updating issues when networks down fixed #83

* Version 0.4.0 -- 2011-06-30

	* Url shortening service enable, with ur1.ca and bit.ly
	* Date appends to tweets when older than the current day
	* Lowercase enable in config for control-sequence - thanks quite
	* Default value for refresh set to 3 minutes
	* New filter system, allow to filter tweets without urls, and lots
	  customisazion on it
	* Input box moves to the bottom
	* Open user avatar with feh (customizable)
	* lazzy loading of tweets when scroll down, cycle to infinyte
	* Lots of documentation update and review, thank jasonwryan

